    {
      "id": "b-001",
      "mode": "hook",
      "speakerNote": "Energetic, look to camera. Say the Thai phrase like you're talking to a taxi driver.",
      "imageRef": "img-001",
      "lines": [
        {
          "id": "l-0001",
          "lang": "th",
          "thai": "ไปสยามค่ะ",
          "translit": "bpai sa-yǎam khâ",
          "display": "immediate",
          "spoken": true
        },
        {
          "id": "l-0002",
          "lang": "en",
          "english": "Go to Siam, please.",
          "display": "delayed-1s",
          "spoken": false
        },
        {
          "id": "l-0003",
          "lang": "en",
          "english": "Today you'll learn everything you need to take a taxi in Bangkok.",
          "display": "delayed-2s",
          "spoken": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "b-002",
      "mode": "explain",
      "speakerNote": "Conversational, personal. Tell your story about the Bangkok taxi scam. Laugh about it — it's a rite of passage.",
      "imageRef": "img-001",
      "lines": [
        {
          "id": "l-0004",
          "lang": "en",
          "english": "OK, story time. The first taxi I ever took in Bangkok, the driver looked at me and said 'two hundred baht'. I had no idea if that was a lot or a little — so I said yes. Turns out the meter would have been sixty baht. I paid three times the price because I didn't know one phrase.",
          "display": "immediate",
          "spoken": true
        },
        {
          "id": "l-0005",
          "lang": "th",
          "thai": "เปิดมิเตอร์ด้วยค่ะ",
          "translit": "bpèrt mí-dtêr dûuay khâ",
          "display": "immediate",
          "spoken": true
        },
        {
          "id": "l-0006",
          "lang": "en",
          "english": "That phrase right there would have saved me 140 baht. Let's make sure it doesn't happen to you.",
          "display": "immediate",
          "spoken": true
        }
      ]
    },
